HEADWORD: Rooftree
<hw>Roof"tree`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The beam in the
angle of a roof; hence, the roof itself.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Now for me the woods may wither, now for me the
<qex>rooftree</qex> fall.</q> <rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Roofy</ent>⟦br⟧
